Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Trafalgar Law and \Nhave come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But caught up in the current \Nking Doflamingo's agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were trapped along \Nwith the entire island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On top of that, he put prices on \Nthe heads of Luffy and 11 others,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now they're being hunted \Nby all the citizens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with the Straw Hats fighting \Nthe Don Quixote Family fiercely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Law finally got to the Royal Palace\Nwhere Doflamingo is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick his ass now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! I told you it's our ultimate stratagem!\NI also told you not to get heated!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:04:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do it now! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Red Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Radio Knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}! You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Noble Family!\NThe True Identity of Doflamingo!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Doffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Law, you fool!\NYou're not gonna get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Straw Hat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite a blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?! It didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That strategy will never work again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shitty brats!\NYou're messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake one, again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no business with the fake-mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an all-or-nothing gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm determined to bet my life on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose your dice,\Nthe game is over before you can even roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?\NAre you listening, Sabo-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie! You're not listening at all!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been absent-minded the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! You have a position now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get emotional\Nand fight a guy like the Navy admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna lead\Nthe Revolutionary Army into war?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's in danger! I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You should!\N--{\i1}Nah{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna get dragged into a mess\Nby your recklessness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--{\i1}Scrwew iwt!{\i0}\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An' dat{\i0} guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are birds of a feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Navy and Doflamingo are both\Nout of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy will never be a hero\Nin this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If somebody notices that's \Nwhat you're thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just being blocked by you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sort of a lucky man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?!\NUnderstood?! Were you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah... boh... -{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you always like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do what you like\Nwhile others are worried
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about you like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Hack and I are forced \Nto clean up your mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your babysitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hack and I always get chewed out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbecause of your selfish actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Admiral Fujitora, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lure the other criminals\Nusing these criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's move on with the luring plan!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop!\N--Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 500 million prize - God Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll kill him and make a name \Nfor our pirate group instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec! They're important hostages\Nto end the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your hypocrisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same if you hand \Nthem over to Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain... Let's kick all of their asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-Help!\N--Do it! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help... Please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt those citizens anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to do that, fight me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shithead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tank! Hack! I need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:10:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You didn't get hurt?\N--N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good!\N--King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kill King Riku!\N--Kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you guys lay a finger\Non the citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}, we got them all.\N--Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts, doesn't it?\NI'll give you first aid for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old King Riku, he's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I really am! No! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm free!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, is it okay to release us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a decade, we were holding \Na grudge against King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was just manipulated by \NDoflamingo for one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we didn't even notice that \Nwe had lost our loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We praised the king who was a pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even after we learned the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Neven after we learned the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were still looking for salvation\Nin the game he started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know\Nwhat we're doing anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to this country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}... please save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What happened to them?!\N--What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\NWhat are we supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell us to fight, we'll take up arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\N--We'll follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we wait... for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be too late to choose death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are they so important to you?!\NThey're pirates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're unlawful men - who will break\Nthis country's deceptive peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father-sama, I decided to trust them,\Nthe Straw Hat Pirates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At least, the words of Straw \NHat and the others are humane{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and they take actions\Nout of the goodness of their hearts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have been believing in Luffy-kun and \Nthe others' victory without realizing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Admiral Fujitora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressrosa was once the symbol of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get involved in a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Why the hell is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting on the same one as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the "Straw" and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at this country!\NIf I stop now, what's gonna happen to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Long-Range Attack! Bagworm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand-and-Eighty Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mingo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mingo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullet String!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullet String!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Doffy! That serves him right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law! I know all about your ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the ability of the Op-Op Fruit was\Nsomething we sought in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I got chopped up,\NI'm gonna turn back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Radio Knife is a different cutting method\Nfrom my regular Amputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For several minutes, even with any \Ntreatment or ability, your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't be reassembled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help my nose running!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop snotting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget that I used \Nto treat you kindly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Injection!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Snot Blade-Catcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the finisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fallbright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who\Nmesses with my Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember\Nwhat I hate the most, Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be looked down upon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Suddenly, my body gets...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:19:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bella...\N--Dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could take me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that shitty brats \Nlike you guys got conceited
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thought even for a second, \Nthat you could defeat me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an unbearable humiliation to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:20:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a descendent of the noblest \Nbloodlines in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're admirable just by \Nthe fact of our birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to possess the most \Nunobtainable power in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one day, my father abandoned \Nthe greatest power
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the world that we were born with,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the four of us in the family...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...descended to this manure-pile world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that "live like human-beings" bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was an idiotic man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's live a humble life here,\Nall four of us as a family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Where are the slaves-{\i1}eh{\i0}?!\NLet's go buy some-{\i1}eh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, why don't they fall \Ndown on their knees-{\i1}eh{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Why do they come after us-{\i1}eh{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a Celestial Dragon family!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill them... Make them suffer \Nfor the rest of their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the age of ten,\NI'd seen heaven and hell on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I killed my father\Nwho caused all that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returned to Mariejois with his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.66,0:22:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Celestial Dragons in heaven\Nwould never accept a renegade family!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew there was no way \Nto get out of this hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI swore to myself at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I will destroy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...every single thing in the world\Nthat they dominate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The life I've lived was\Non a very different level from yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time to play around...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Facing Doflamingo, possessor of such
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,great power that he can even move \Nthe World Government to action,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Law are left helpless!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When their execution is \Nfinally about to begin,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the world-shaking, tremendous \Nsecret of the Op-Op Fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand Law's shocking past will be revealed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Ultimate Power! The \NSecret of the Op-Op Fruit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
